data.description: Come see this well appointed 5 bedroom 3 bath home on over an acre in the desired subdivision of Hackberry Heights in Van Alstyne. This Open concept home boasts lots of natural light, high ceilings and a fantastic layout. Natural wood floors and tile throughout, with carpet in all bedrooms. Central Heat & Air replaced in 2018. Over-sized 3 car garage with a carport and lots of extra parking. Energy efficient windows throughout. The backyard is a low maintenance private paradise with synthetic turf surrounding the heated saltwater infinity pool and spa. Home has so many extras and the owners have included with the sale: security cameras, ring doorbell, and TV mounts.  In addition the Generator and Gun Safe convey. A MUST SEE WITH ALL THE EXTRAS!!
